OL,3,CMixed Bank Holiday weather leaves
OL,4,Cbusiness owners worried about trade
OL,6,FBusiness owners across Wales have been
OL,7,Fcounting the cost of the mixed weather
OL,8,Fthis Bank Holiday as rain and cooler
OL,9,Ftemperatures may have turned visitors
OL,10,Faway from seaside resorts.
OL,12,FResearch released by the Welsh
OL,13,Fgovernment earlier this year found
OL,14,Fthat more than a third of Welsh
OL,15,Ftourism businesses had fewer customers
OL,16,Fthis June compared to last year.
OL,18,FPoor weather had been flagged as a top
OL,19,Fconcern among business owners in the
OL,20,Ftourism sector, according to the Wales
OL,21,FTourism Business Barometer 2024.
