OL,3,CMixed Bank Holiday weather leaves
OL,4,Cbusiness owners worried about trade
OL,6,FGiovanni Zeraschi, a business owner in
OL,7,FBarry Island, told ITV Wales on Monday
OL,8,Fthat the weather is "all-important."
OL,10,FHe said: "You've got to get the sunny,
OL,11,Fwarm weather...
OL,13,F"If it's blowing a gale, pouring with
OL,14,Frain, then you just know you cut down
OL,15,Fon the staff, you've got to cut down
OL,16,Fon the costs, and you know you've got
OL,17,Fto have a very short working day...
OL,19,F"And obviously that affects the
OL,20,Fincome."
