OL,3,CMixed Bank Holiday weather leaves
OL,4,Cbusiness owners worried about trade
OL,6,FIt has been a "rocky" start to the
OL,7,Fyear for many businesses, according to
OL,8,FNicky Williamson of Wales Tourism
OL,9,FAlliance.
OL,11,FShe said there was a "huge amount of
OL,12,Femphasis" on this Bank Holiday as a
OL,13,Ffinal push for trade before the winter.
OL,15,FThe slow start to the year is
OL,16,Freflected across all four regions of
OL,17,FWales, with other seaside resorts like
OL,18,FLlandudno also likely to be impacted
OL,19,Fby the gloomy summer weather.
