OL,3,CMixed Bank Holiday weather leaves
OL,4,Cbusiness owners worried about trade
OL,6,FBad forecasts can lead to not only a
OL,7,Flack of last minute bookings, but also
OL,8,Fthe cancellation of existing bookings.
OL,10,F42% of caravan parks in Wales say they
OL,11,Fhave been particularly concerned about
OL,12,Fthe weather, according to the Wales
OL,13,FTourism Business Barometer.
OL,15,FThe latest research shows attractions
OL,16,Fhave been the best performing sector,
OL,17,Fwith 25% having more customers this
OL,18,Fyear to date than last year and 23%
OL,19,Fhaving fewer.
